data.text: The main thread with all earlier movie threads: https://t.co/Mww9JX6JgS

Chadwick Boseman (2014: James Brown in Get on Up) plays a musician, who gets kissed by a rabid fangirl, played by Kristen Stewart (2014: Clouds of Sils Maria; Still Alice). We know Chadwick Boseman as T'Challa / Black Panther in Avengers: Infinity War. https://t.co/NkghCfl9F1

9 Kisses features two famliar faces: David Oyelowo (2014: Martin Luther King in Selma), who we know from Spooks (as Danny Hunter) and Small Island (as Gilbert), arm wrestles with Timothy Spall (2014: Mr. Turner). https://t.co/B0Rh3E4FUG
